summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 36E page 103, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Lots 1-7, incl., and Lots 19-24, incl., all in Block B, Phinney Addition, from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM) Zone, located on the south side of East Highland Drive between Broadway North and Harvard Ave. No.
